        "ggV6ZWJnxHY_text": "<p>I drink this every morning before work and it keeps me focused for hours. No jitters like coffee gives me.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>— Daniel M.</strong></span></p>",
        "ggZY2m7frnT_text": "<p>The Ginger &amp; Lemongrass flavor is so refreshing. I feel lighter and more energized throughout the day.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>— Priya S.</strong></span></p>"
      },
